###
    NEOVIM FILETREE SHORTCUTS
    by luca
###


# Command	Description
<leader>e   open the filetree inside neovim


# Actions   Description
    a | create new file
    d | delete file
    c | copy file
    x | cut file
    p | paste file
    r | rename file
    o | open file in new buffer
    v | vertical split
    h | horizontal split
    u | go directory up
    q | quit filetree
    l | refresh filetree
    


